extendedInfo.description: Y5 Drive is a App which allow you stream Media and Document files from Pretec Wi-Fi Storage products. It allows 8 mobile devices stream 4 videos at the same time. It's easy to setup and powerful features. 1. Login automatically without User Name and Password. 2. Upload/Download (Bi-Direction) 3. Internet Access bridge 4. iOS data sharing 5. Support 1080P HD movie 6. Folder management 7. Export your photo via E-Mail 8. Open In support. Support various media formats.keyword: y5drive, y5 drive, Y5Drive, Y5 Drive
